name: Patterned birds
description:
Print of an original digital illustration done by me. I used retro patterns for the colors of the birds.
The print it's ready to be framed.

The Print measures 29.7cm x 21cm (11.7 in x 8.3 inches)
It is printed onto opal paper with texture, 220gsm, in color white.
The print is ready to be framed.



NOTE: Colors may vary from screen to screen



** The shipment is via Standard service.
